    "causal_summary": "The detached CLI fan-out path had: (1) review init bindings missing from CLI prompts, (2) unrecoverable salvage yielding false-fulfilled lineages, (3) mixed-salvage failures treated as fatal instead of retryable, (4) prompt-only write isolation via unconditional `--dangerously-skip-permissions`, (5) a playbook regression that did not exercise the documented exit-0/no-artifact path, (6) registry-only merge silently skipping leaf-only lineages, and (7) lag-ceiling observability events normalizing to `unknown`",
